{"title": "Appeals Committee", "start_datetime": "2026-11-26 18:00:00", "end_datetime": "2026-11-26 22:00:00", "dtstamp_updated_at_datetime": "2026-07-23 07:55:22", "detail_url": "https://events.burlington.ca/meetings/Detail/2026-11-26-1300-Appeals-Committee", "video_url": null, "agendas": [], "package": [], "meeting_type": "Appeals Committee", "event_details_description": "The Burlington Appeals Committee is an administrative tribunal established by City Council in August 2025 (DGM-57-25).  The Appeals Committee hears appeals from decisions issued by the City related to it’s Licensing By-laws.  It also hears appeals from orders issued by the City related to it’s Property Standards By-law. The Appeals Committee makes final decisions that are not reviewed by City Council.", "contact": null}
