pproval takes place of items that went to the meetings of the Committee of the Whole, Pipeline to Permit Committee, Council Workshop and Audit Committee. Meeting agendas, dates or times may change. To verify information, contact the Office of the City Clerk by email at\nclerks@burlington.ca\nor at 905-335-7777 Ext. 7481. Note: Special meetings of Council may be scheduled as required.", "contact": null}
